metadata.name: Paper Art 3D #142
metadata.description:
Welcome to “Paper Art 3D”

“Paper Art 3D” is the beginning of my journey as a new generative art creator. Starting from simple geometrical shapes like a small step towards to something greater in the future. 
It all began from simple 3D shapes that combined into mountains, trees, and houses. Then everything expanded and united into many exotic cityscapes. Each with their own style and uniqueness.

Built with three.js.
- - - - - - - - - - - - - -
Space Bar  --> Save a simple screenshot image of the canvas
Mouse: Drag & Scroll  --> Rotate & Zoom in-out 
- - - - - - - - - - - - - -

metadata.name: TRACKS #27
metadata.description:
Meant to be enjoyed gracefully.

Expanding randomly subdivided recursions.

Elements:
few (40% chance), some (40% chance) or quite some (20% chance)

Colors:
168 possible variations.
Either 2, 3 or 4 colors taken from one of 3 palettes (90% chance)
Or one special palette with all colors mixed (10% chance)
6 background colors. 

Press ’s’ to save image (only works when animation has stopped).
Press ’p’ to switch between pixel perfect, margined or regular display.
Press ’f’ to toggle fullscreen.

This work is licensed under CC BY-NC 4.0
